Ian Somerhalder https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ian_Somerhalder 0 Ian Joseph Somerhalder (born December 8, 1978) is an American actor, model and director. He is known for playing Boone Carlyle in the TV drama Lost and Damon Salvatore in The CW's supernatural drama The Vampire Diaries.
